timeline.bodyText:
@olegmoz maybe it'd be better to use yaml-library which throws exception when yaml-path is not found?
In this case this method could've been simplified into something like:
return Yaml.createYamlInput(this.source)
    .readYamlMapping()
    .get("meta")
    .get("storage");

